{"tid":1041110,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"2019 Sony 攝影獎公開組出爐 香港女子奪組別冠軍 拍攝的是她創作的樹脂藝術品","createTime":"2019-02-28T14:47:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T12:36:15.000Z","uid":50196,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2cc1babe9cee0c9a92261ab3508a1522cff20e44","tid":1041110,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T14:47:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/sony_open_Still-Life.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2Fsony_open_Still-Life.jpg&h=7281ca7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第 12 屆 Sony 世界攝影獎公開組及區域獎的得獎名單近日已經出爐，公開組分為建築、文化、創意等 10 個組別，各組別的第一名將會角逐「The Open Photographer of the Year」的名譽。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在公開組入面，本港攝影師 Rachel Yee Laam Lai 憑作品「Peony and Leaves」（上圖）贏得靜物組第一名。她是一位自學業餘攝影師，而作品拍攝的是她創作的樹脂藝術品，她先將自製的塗料與樹脂混合，再用微距攝影來捕捉混合物從液態轉為固態時的顏色變化。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://photoblog.hk/249399/2019sony世界攝影獎公開組得獎名單出爐，香港攝影師-yee-laam/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2F249399%2F2019sony%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%94%9D%E5%BD%B1%E7%8D%8E%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E7%B5%84%E5%BE%97%E7%8D%8E%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E5%87%BA%E7%88%90%EF%BC%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%94%9D%E5%BD%B1%E5%B8%AB-yee-laam%2F&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMPUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=fedeba65\" target=\"_blank\">https://photoblog.hk/249399/2019sony世界攝影獎公開組得獎名單出爐，香港攝影師-yee-laam/</a>"},{"pid":"0ebe6e6dce62d17ed3c22e6a1f4e05acb7e41033","tid":1041110,"uid":191921,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T14:49:31.000Z","msg":"相機公司搞個d 比賽。。。。。。點撚審美的"},{"pid":"175d19cef6df00632ce70547e2e78ae68d4f573d","tid":1041110,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T14:50:05.000Z","msg":"高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hk